Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:35.70,Takagi san—Picture 03-1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1552.4,382.4)}{\fad(300,300)}团扇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:38.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:39.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天你来的挺早嘛  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早上好  高木同学也很早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:45.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天估计会很热
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:48.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就乘着阳光还不强的时候赶紧来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:49.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:52.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我今早是被热醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明明马上就要到十月了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:00.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:03.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:11.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你带了个挺不错的东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:18.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好凉快  还好把它带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:22.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么样高木同学  羡慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:26.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看着我凉快的样子  为自己的准备不足而懊悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说  给我也扇扇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:32.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,凭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:34.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为很热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:37.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我也很热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我们比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:42.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我要是赢了  你就给我扇风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以是可以  要是我赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我就给西片扇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:02:59.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:04.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那  我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:09.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,橡皮擦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:13.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,用你的团扇  让橡皮擦移动得更远的人赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:18.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那你先来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,移动得更远的人赢么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这是要比拼体力和力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:31.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,优势在我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:39.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,给我动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:47.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,给我动给我动…给我动啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学  见识到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:57.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你看到了吗  刚刚橡皮动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,刚刚动了一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:11.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真没想到这样也能让橡皮移动  真让人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:16.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来如此  她觉得我没法扇动橡皮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:20.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,假装要比赛  其实想让我给她扇风对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好了  这会轮到高木同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:24.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:37.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我移的比你远
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:44.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:51.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我只是说  用团扇让橡皮移动更多的人赢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么  给我扇风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:14.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,本来应该是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样的话  西片也能凉快一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你手停了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你看起来很热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为我在扇扇子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:58.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且刚才我用尽全力扇了扇子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,靠近一点会更凉快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:11.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你手又停了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:14.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好热好热
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,热得简直是气候异常了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好热  好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:34.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,主人公特别热血  有个很厉害的魔球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,几乎就是战斗漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:40.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,教练虽然严厉但热爱棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,经理则是意外受伤而隐退的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还有最强的劲敌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,总之是很有趣的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真让人欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:03.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对对  就是这个招式最帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这个动作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是要用那个招式了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没错  正是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,魔球  时间穿梭…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:47.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你刚刚是不是在耍酷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:52.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶  我太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:57.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她一定是听到了昨天的对话  故意把乒乓球丢出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,竟然准备得如此周密  可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:06.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,呃  这件事还请你务必保密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:26.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,感觉挺有意思的  我也想玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你要是能让我三振出局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就帮你保密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:34.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么  开局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,必须要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对了  你模仿一下漫画嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就像刚才那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:51.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我才不学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:56.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽说如此  但是为了集中精力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还是需要想象一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:02.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好了  打者只剩一名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:06.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片选手离梦寐以求的胜利只有一步之遥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可是打者是他的宿敌  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:14.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,过去的交手记录  竟然是高木同学全胜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,二和三
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:19.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  先投一个坏球观察情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:22.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:24.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,让你见识见识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.00,Takagi san—Picture 03-2,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1766,542)}{\fad(250,300)}交给你了  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然严厉但热爱棒球的田边教练
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:35.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}要是我没受伤就能投球了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,意外受伤而隐退  成为经理的高尾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:36.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,加油  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,放松心态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我们陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,至今为止遇到的伙伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我要把对你们的感谢注入这一球里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:53.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,魔球  时间穿梭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好戏才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你说的是漫画的台词吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一不小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好了好了  第二球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:15.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,糟了  想象消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我居然犯了这种失误
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,总之  只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,时间穿梭  魔球…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,错了  是魔球时间穿梭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我打
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,全垒打
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这也是漫画的桥段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是我的桥段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那个  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:11.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我刚刚悄悄做的事情  千万不要告诉大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:21.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想想…作为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,把那本讲棒球的漫画借我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:30.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:36.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不知道你看了会不会觉得有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:37.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:42.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片喜欢的东西  我都想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,等我看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:49.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再像刚才一样代入到里面的角色和我比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:53.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我刚刚才没有代入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明明差不多到该换冬季制服的季节了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:07.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么时候才能凉快下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:09.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,蝉鸣也吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有猫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:18.46,Takagi san—Picture 03-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(430,346)}{\fad(300,360)}解救猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:22.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你还真是喜欢猫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明明养的是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,小胖墩  快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:34.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,快点快点  快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:35.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,似乎对你没兴趣  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:46.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,它是不是卡住了动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}猫咪真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也可能是我的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:56.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,确实  看上去像是动弹不得的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,绝对是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那是寻求帮助的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:03.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,小猫咪等着啊  我这就救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,够不着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:11.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,让开  我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,友加里的话没准能够着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,又退后了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为友加里很吓人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你这话很多余哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,加油友加里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,够到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:34.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没够着  但我自己也卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,等着  这就救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:40.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好痛  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要拉你就温柔点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能缓缓地把头拉出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:47.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:51.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是的  这简直是兄弟争雁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这意思好像不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,诶  那应该是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,河童亦有溺水之时？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谁是河童啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,硬要说的话应该是偷鸡不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊  我出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:07.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:13.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怪不得蝉安静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,找个地方躲雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:19.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看来是场骤雨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都没带伞  糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:30.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,刚才那只猫咪不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:40.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这只猫  是从刚才的墙壁夹缝中出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看来它不是小胖墩  只是长得毛茸茸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:53.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来不是被卡住动不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么嘛  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我还想抓住它撸个爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,总有事与愿违的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天也下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:28.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我又忘带雨衣来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:30.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,雨衣亦有溺水之时呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「河童」与「雨衣」发音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是这样用的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:38.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:40.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,天气预报还说不一定会下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:45.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不好  我忘带雨伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:52.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这下只能淋成落汤鸡回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  我还有最终手段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么大家回去时小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:01.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.86,Takagi san—Picture 03-4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(984,220)\frz15.75\frx12\fry342}办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:17.58,Takagi san—Picture 03-5,,0,0,0,,{\pos(552,838)}失物招领
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:13.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有失物的雨伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只有一把…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:19.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,请借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:21.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,在这里写上年级和姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:26.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,幸好还有伞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然颜色有点让人难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:37.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要是让她知道我忘记带伞…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,欸  要跟我撑同一把伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:43.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哇  你在害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就会变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,拜托了  让我躲一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:51.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以哦  不过你要教我数学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学…已经回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:07.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说起来我都没打招呼就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:17.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天我有赶紧回家的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为再过一会儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:24.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,「爆裂！最强足球」跟「夏日棒球」的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,特别联动节目就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:30.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,足球和棒球的名将们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一起进行踢技比试简直燃爆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,作为铁粉可不容错过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不过大意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下次即使天气预报不确定也带上伞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:48.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能拿到最后的一把伞我还是走运的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,带了伞没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,算了  毕竟是高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:09.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,应该有带吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:11.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但上次  高木同学就忘带了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:26.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道她今天也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:38.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,正因为忘过一次  她今天才不会忘带吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:39.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,毕竟是高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还是赶快回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看「爆裂足球」跟「夏日棒球」的特别节目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  就这么办  就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:05.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,雨  还会停吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:27.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道你…忘带伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:29.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那  要不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:47.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:49.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你在写作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:50.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,觉得等等雨也许就停了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:54.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就打发下时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说起来  西片借到伞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:05.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,班会一结束就冲出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:08.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你是去失物招领处借伞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:09.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:13.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,幸运地借到了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:15.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:21.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以说…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:27.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一起走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:32.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真高兴呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:40.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片竟然邀请我合撑一把伞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,捉弄你是不对的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,毕竟你好心回来接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你肩膀淋湿了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:59.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你是担心我才回来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:03.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这个…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:07.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明明很想看特别节目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:09.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:13.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只要是西片的事我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:38.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下次雨天我要不要故意不带伞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:43.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到时你还会邀我撑一把伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:47.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以是可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:50.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:53.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片很想跟我合撑一把伞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:57.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你不是才说不捉弄我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊抱歉  成习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:02.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,给我好好记得带伞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:04.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:24.32,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}もっと遊んで　指を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:27.24,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}呼んでいる声がするわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:33.87,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}本当も嘘も　興味がないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:37.25,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}指先からすり抜けてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:40.25,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}欲張りな笑い声も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:46.97,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ごちゃ混ぜにした　スープに溶かすから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:53.72,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}音に合わせて　靴をならして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:58.94,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}あたしだけの秘密の場所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:06.94,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}走る雲の影を飛び越えるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:12.70,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}夏の匂い追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:19.21,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}あぁ夢はいつまでも覚めない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:24.67,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}歌う風のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:24.32,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}再多玩玩  打个响指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:27.24,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}听到了你的呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:33.87,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}无论是真是假  我都不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:37.25,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}指尖悄然滑过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:40.25,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}畅怀发出的笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:46.97,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}都乱七八糟地溶进浓汤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:53.72,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}配合着声音  用鞋子打着节拍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:58.94,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}只属于自己的秘密地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:06.94,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}飞身越过那流云的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:12.70,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}追逐着夏日的芳香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:19.21,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}啊啊  一直在美梦中无尽徜徉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:24.67,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}犹如讴歌的风儿一般
